{
  "info": {
    "name": "API Tasks",
    "description": "Gerenciador de Tarefas — Laravel 13 + Sanctum + Spatie ACL",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"company_name\": \"Minha Empresa\",\n  \"name\": \"João Silva\",\n  \"email\": \"joao@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password\",\n  \"password_confirmation\": \"password\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Cria uma nova **empresa (tenant)** e o usuário que a registra como **admin** dela. O token é salvo automaticamente na variável `token`.\n\n**Campos:**\n- `company_name` (obrigatório) — nome da empresa\n- `name`, `email`, `password`, `password_confirmation` (obrigatórios)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Autentica o usuário e retorna um token Sanctum. Salvo automaticamente em `token`.\n\n**Usuários de seed (2 empresas demo):**\n- Example Inc: `admin@example.com` / `user@example.com`\n- Acme Ltda: `admin@acme.com` / `user@acme.com`\n\nSenha de todos: `password`. Cada empresa só enxerga os próprios dados."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Retorna os dados do usuário autenticado com suas roles."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Revoga o token atual do usuário."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Tasks",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Tasks",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tasks?status=pending&priority=high&per_page=15",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "status",
                  "value": "pending",
                  "description": "Filtro: pending | in_progress | completed",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "priority",
                  "value": "high",
                  "description": "Filtro: low | medium | high",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "per_page",
                  "value": "15",
                  "description": "Itens por página (padrão: 15)",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista tarefas com paginação. Sempre restrito à empresa do usuário autenticado.\n- **Admin**: vê todas as tarefas da empresa\n- **User**: vê apenas as próprias tarefas\n\n**Filtros disponíveis:** `status`, `priority`, `per_page`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Task",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Implementar autenticação\",\n  \"description\": \"Adicionar login com OAuth2 ao sistema\",\n  \"status\": \"pending\",\n  \"priority\": \"high\",\n  \"due_date\": \"2026-12-31\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tasks",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks"]
            },
            "description": "Cria uma nova tarefa vinculada ao usuário autenticado.\n\n**Campos:**\n- `title` (obrigatório)\n- `description` (opcional)\n- `status`: `pending` | `in_progress` | `completed` (padrão: `pending`)\n- `priority`: `low` | `medium` | `high` (padrão: `medium`)\n- `due_date`: data ISO (opcional, deve ser >= hoje)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Task",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tasks/1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks", "1"]
            },
            "description": "Retorna uma tarefa específica.\n- **Admin**: pode ver qualquer tarefa\n- **User**: pode ver apenas as próprias tarefas"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Task",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Implementar autenticação OAuth2\",\n  \"status\": \"in_progress\",\n  \"priority\": \"high\",\n  \"due_date\": \"2026-12-31\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tasks/1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks", "1"]
            },
            "description": "Atualiza parcialmente uma tarefa (todos os campos são opcionais).\n- **Admin**: pode atualizar qualquer tarefa\n- **User**: pode atualizar apenas as próprias tarefas"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Task",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tasks/1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks", "1"]
            },
            "description": "Remove uma tarefa.\n- **Admin**: pode deletar qualquer tarefa\n- **User**: pode deletar apenas as próprias tarefas"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users (Admin)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Users",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/users?per_page=15",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "users"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "per_page",
                  "value": "15",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista os usuários **da empresa** com suas roles. **Apenas admin.**"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/users/1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "users", "1"]
            },
            "description": "Retorna os dados de um usuário específico. **Apenas admin.**"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update User",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Nome Atualizado\",\n  \"email\": \"novo@example.com\",\n  \"role\": \"admin\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/users/2",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "users", "2"]
            },
            "description": "Atualiza dados e/ou role de um usuário. **Apenas admin.**\n\n**Campos:**\n- `name` (opcional)\n- `email` (opcional)\n- `role`: `admin` | `user` (opcional — troca a role do usuário)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete User",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/users/2",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "users", "2"]
            },
            "description": "Remove um usuário. **Apenas admin.** Um admin não pode deletar a si mesmo."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
